                                programme</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://wildcodeschool.fr/candidat/">Comment candidater</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://wildcodeschool.fr/faq/">FAQ</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-xs-3 nosecoles">
